data.description: Looking for your next Florida Vacation Home, Investment Property or Primary Home? Look no further! This Beautiful fully furnished 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom Townhome Located within the highly sought-after gated Resort-Style Reunion Resort Community is A Must See! This Beautiful Home has an **Active Resort Membership** and an **Active Golf Membership** which are both transferable and located adjacent to the 18-Hole Jack Nicklaus designed Golf Course and Clubhouse. This amenity rich community includes a waterpark, lazy river, multiple pools, restaurants, miniature-golf, pickle-ball, tennis, bocce ball, foot golf, walking trails and playgrounds. When you step inside this amazing home, you will instantly fall in love and be blown away by the high ceilings and oversized doors. The Gourmet Kitchen includes lots of counter space with a lot of room to cook amazing meals and entertain. The Kitchen is equipped with quartz countertops, stainless appliances, and upgraded cabinets. The open floor plan provides ample space for entertaining and has ceramic tile throughout the first floor. There is also a half bath conveniently located adjacent to the Kitchen. As you proceed to the 2nd floor, you will feel as though you have transported into an unbelievable  Disney Palace. Each of the 3 spacious custom bedrooms includes a unique Disney Theme and is gorgeously decorated. The Master bedroom with a walk-in closet, includes an Ensuite Bathroom with dual vanities and a walk-in shower. For your convenience, the Laundry Room is located on the second floor next to the third bathroom. Enjoy quiet mornings and afternoons on the screen-enclosed lanai, which is a perfect place to relax with a cup of coffee in the morning or your favorite glass of wine at night. Reunion Resort is a 2,300 acre Resort and Golf Community with three championship signature golf courses, a multimillion dollar waterpark located just a few miles away from all of the Disney and Universal Studios Themed Parks. It is only a mere 20 minutes to the Orlando International Airport and easily accessible to the major highways. Welcome Home!
